ast 1 daughter. He died in his hometown."},"et":{"Abt 1120–":"umbes 1120–Surnud","1120–Male":"1120–Surnud","1150–1184":"1150–1184","1108–1154":"1108–1154","Abt 1120":"umbes 1120","1154":"1154","1120":"1120","1184":"1184","1150":"1150","1108":"1108","Wormhill, Chapel en le Frith, Derbyshire, England":"Wormhill, Derbyshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1120–":"noin 1120–Kuollut","1120–Male":"1120–Kuollut","1150–1184":"1150–1184","1108–1154":"1108–1154","Abt 1120":"noin 1120","1154":"1154","1120":"1120","1184":"1184","1150":"1150","1108":"1108","Wormhill, Chapel en le Frith, Derbyshire, England":"Wormhill, Derbyshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1120–":"environ 1120–Décédé","1120–Male":"1120–Décédé","1150–1184":"1150–1184","1108–1154":"1108–1154","Abt 1120":"environ 1120","1154":"1154","1120":"1120","1184":"1184","1150":"1150","1108":"1108","Wormhill, Chapel en le Frith, Derbyshire, England":"Wormhill, Derbyshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Thomas FitzHerbert est né environ 1120, à Wormhill, Derbyshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de Herbert Fitzherbert. Il a eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"Abt 1120–":"um 1120–Verstorben","1120–Male":"1120–Verstorben","1150–1184":"1150–1184","1108–1154":"1108–1154","Abt 1120":"um 1120","1154":"1154","1120":"1120","1184":"1184","1150":"1150","1108":"1108","Wormhill, Chapel en le Frith, Derbyshire, England":"Wormhill, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Thomas FitzHerbert wurde um 1120 in Wormhill, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom, als Sohn von Herbert Fitzherbert geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Tochter. Er starb in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"Abt 1120–":"about 1120–Desede","1120–Male":"1120–Desede","1150–1184":"1150–1184","1108–1154":"1108–1154","Abt 1120":"about 1120","1154":"1154","1120":"1120","1184":"1184","1150":"1150","1108":"1108","Wormhill, Chapel en le Frith, Derbyshire, England":"Wormhill, Derbyshire, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu"